    {
      "title": "Simplify the function",
      "content": "Inside the absolute value,<br/>$$x-5x=-4x$$<br/>So<br/>$$f(x)=|-4x|=4|x|$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Use the given equation",
      "content": "First evaluate $f(6)$:<br/>$$f(6)=4|6|=24$$<br/>Then use $f(6)-f(a)=-24$:<br/>$$24-f(a)=-24$$<br/>$$f(a)=48$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for the input",
      "content": "Since $f(a)=4|a|$,<br/>$$4|a|=48$$<br/>$$|a|=12$$<br/>The choices include $12$, not $-12$. The answer is <strong>C</strong>."
    }
  ]
}
